<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Nettleton, Asahel (1783-1844), Robinson, Robert (1735-1790)</author>
<hymn_number>550</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ya Ubangiji mun gode
 Don ka sake tada mu
 Har ka tara mu gabanka
 Don mu furta yabonmu.
 Cikin dukan duhun dare
 Kana nan tare da mu,
 Ba abin da ya same mu
 Tun da kana tsaronmu.</lyrics>
<title>Ya Ubangiji Mun Gode, Don Ka Sake Tada Mu LW550</title>
</song>